'''Ho'Din''' was the [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Dins]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Moltok/Legends|Moltok]]. Its spoken form included an amount of croaks and hisses. The [[Ho'Din writing|written form]] of Ho'Din included characters derived from the shapes of Moltok [[Plant/Legends|flora]]. Ho'Din lexicon includes a great amount of plant-based idioms and metaphors. The name "Ho'Din" meant 'walking flower' in the language.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

